COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_staking_validator_history.jailed IS 'jailed defined whether the validator has been jailed from bonded status or not.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_staking_validator_history.status IS 'status is the validator status (bonded/unbonding/unbonded).';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_staking_validator_history.tokens IS 'tokens define the delegated tokens (incl. self-delegation).';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_staking_validator_history.delegator_shares IS 'delegator_shares defines total shares issued to a validator''s delegators.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_staking_validator_history.description IS 'description defines the description terms for the validator.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_staking_validator_history.unbonding_height IS 'unbonding_height defines, if unbonding, the height at which this validator has begun unbonding.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_staking_validator_history.unbonding_time IS 'unbonding_time defines, if unbonding, the min time for the validator to complete unbonding.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_staking_validator_history.commission IS 'commission defines the commission parameters.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_staking_validator_history.min_self_delegation IS 'min_self_delegation is the validator''s self declared minimum self delegation.  Since: cosmos-sdk 0.46';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_staking_validator_history.unbonding_on_hold_ref_count IS 'strictly positive if this validator''s unbonding has been stopped by external modules';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_staking_validator_history.unbonding_ids IS 'list of unbonding ids, each uniquely identifing an unbonding of this validator';

