COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.id IS 'id defines the unique id of the proposal.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.messages IS 'messages are the arbitrary messages to be executed if the proposal passes.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.status IS 'status defines the proposal status.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.final_tally_result IS 'final_tally_result is the final tally result of the proposal. When querying a proposal via gRPC, this field is not populated until the proposal''s voting period has ended.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.submit_time IS 'submit_time is the time of proposal submission.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.deposit_end_time IS 'deposit_end_time is the end time for deposition.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.total_deposit_amount IS 'total_deposit is the total deposit on the proposal.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.total_deposit_denom IS 'total_deposit is the total deposit on the proposal.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.voting_start_time IS 'voting_start_time is the starting time to vote on a proposal.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.voting_end_time IS 'voting_end_time is the end time of voting on a proposal.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.metadata IS 'metadata is any arbitrary metadata attached to the proposal. the recommended format of the metadata is to be found here: https://docs.cosmos.network/v0.47/modules/gov#proposal-3';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.title IS 'title is the title of the proposal  Since: cosmos-sdk 0.47';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.summary IS 'summary is a short summary of the proposal  Since: cosmos-sdk 0.47';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.proposer IS 'proposer is the address of the proposal sumbitter  Since: cosmos-sdk 0.47';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.expedited IS 'expedited defines if the proposal is expedited  Since: cosmos-sdk 0.50';
COMMENT ON COLUMN cosmos_gov_proposal_history.failed_reason IS 'failed_reason defines the reason why the proposal failed  Since: cosmos-sdk 0.50';

